---
import DownloadCards from "../components/DownloadCards.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import {
  cudaSidecar,
  downloads,
  updateManifestUrl,
  version,
  windowsInstaller,
} from "../data";
---

<BaseLayout title="下载 - 如是我闻 Rushi">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">下载 · v{version}</span>
    <h1>下载如是我闻桌面版</h1>
    <p>
      当前正式包为 v{version}，托管于 updates.rushi.app。Windows 推荐下载离线安装包 zip；macOS 提供 Apple Silicon DMG。
      每个安装包旁附有 SHA256 校验文件，便于核对完整性。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-block">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2>主下载</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">日常分发请优先使用下列入口。</p>
    </div>
    <DownloadCards items={downloads} />
  </section>

  <section class="section-block muted">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2>其他资产</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">安装包 EXE、更新清单与可选 GPU 侧车。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-grid download-extra">
      <article>
        <h2>{windowsInstaller.title}</h2>
        <p>{windowsInstaller.meta}</p>
        <p>{windowsInstaller.note}</p>
        <div class="download-extra-actions">
          <a class="button primary" href={windowsInstaller.href}>{windowsInstaller.actionLabel}</a>
          <a class="download-checksum" href={windowsInstaller.checksum}>SHA256 校验文件</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>应用内更新清单</h2>
        <p>安装版会读取官方 OTA 清单，确认后下载、验签并安装。手动检查入口在设置的关于页。</p>
        <div class="download-extra-actions">
          <a class="button secondary" href={updateManifestUrl}>打开 latest.json</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>{cudaSidecar.title}</h2>
        <p>{cudaSidecar.note}</p>
        <div class="download-extra-actions">
          <a class="button secondary" href={cudaSidecar.href}>CUDA 侧车地址</a>
        </div>
        <small>文件就绪前访问可能 404；以应用环境页或 CDN 实际状态为准。</small>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
